Herb Vigran https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herb_Vigran 0 Herbert "Herb" Vigran (June 5, 1910 – November 29, 1986) was an American character actor in Hollywood from the 1930s to the 1980s. Over his 50-year career, he made over 350 television and film appearances.
